xtide: Xtide is a package that provides tide and current predictions in a
xtide: variety of formats.  Graphs, text listings, and calendars can be
xtide: generated, or a tide clock can be provided on your desktop.
xtide: 
xtide: The algorith that xtide uses to predict tides is the one used by the 
xtide: National Ocean Service in the U.S.  It is significantly more accurate
xtide: than the simple tide clocks that can be bought in stores.  However,
xtide: it takes more to predict tides accurately than just an algorithm.
xtide: Xtide uses harmonics files to predict tides.
xtide:
xtide: Homepage: http://www.flaterco.com/xtide/

